r4600 | dbera | 2008-03-09 22:52:26 -0400 (Sun, 09 Mar 2008) | 7 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/beagle/beagled/BeagleDaemon.cs
   M /trunk/beagle/beagled/BuildIndex.cs
