------------------------------------------------------------------------
r4533 | dbera | 2008-02-23 22:26:27 -0500 (Sat, 23 Feb 2008) | 5 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/beagle/tools/Makefile.am
   M /trunk/beagle/tools/Query.cs
   A /trunk/beagle/tools/StaticQuery.cs

Add a tool to query beagle indexes without the daemon (like 'locate'). Meant to be used with static indexes but could be used to any indexes in principle.
$ beagle-static-query query-terms
$ beagle-static-query --backend [+-] <backend-name> query-terms
$ beagle-static-query --add-static-backend <static-backend-name> --backend none query-terms

------------------------------------------------------------------------
