   M /trunk/beagle/Util/Config.cs
   M /trunk/beagle/beagled/BeagleDaemon.cs
   M /trunk/beagle/beagled/BuildIndex.cs

beagled and beagle-build-index will refuse to start if the required global configuration files are not found. It should not be a problem if beagle is properly installed; if running uninstalled, run make install at least once or hand copy the config files.

