------------------------------------------------------------------------
r4088 | dbera | 2007-10-27 10:05:07 -0400 (Sat, 27 Oct 2007) | 6 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/beagle/beagled/Server.cs
   M /trunk/beagle/beagled/Shutdown.cs
   M /trunk/beagle/beagled/webinterface/index.xsl
   M /trunk/beagle/tools/config-files/Networking.xml

index.xsl : revert accidental commit.
others: Add option Networking.WebInterface.
* If Networking.ServiceEnabled is true, WebInterface is ignored. Server accepts connections from anywhere.
* If only WebInterface is true, server accepts connections only from local host.
* WebInterface can be enabled/disabled by "beagle-config Networking WebInterface true/false" even when beagled is running (Networking.ServiceEnabled can't be changed on the fly :( )

------------------------------------------------------------------------
