r4058 | dbera | 2007-10-16 18:32:47 -0400 (Tue, 16 Oct 2007) | 4 lines
Changed paths:
   M /trunk/beagle/Util/ExternalStringsHack.cs.in
   M /trunk/beagle/Util/FSpotTools.cs
